column5: Hi,  First Post Ever - Just looking for some input.  Hoping to get out to the eastern side of Scugog this weekend to do a little walleye fishing.  Most of my time is spent up in Haliburton ice fishing for Lake Trout.  Not looking for anyone's honey holes..I'll gladly put in the legwork myself as I've done before.  Just looking for overall depths and structure as I have some pretty good maps of the lake.  Steve
